      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.nT7Vm4iuPmWBqRvQ]{Immortal Tutor (Su) - Elemental}</p>\n<p>You learn your patron’s third lesson, which grants an additional benefit whenever the first lesson ability is active.</p>\n<p><strong>Third Lesson:&nbsp;</strong> You gain a defense based on your elemental type, with a value equal to 1 plus the spell’s level—electricity resistance (air), DR/piercing (earth), fire resistance (fire), or DR/bludgeoning (water). This DR or resistance stacks with one other source of DR or resistance you already have.</p>\n<p><em>Activate relevent modifier in the Modifier tab, and edit</em><em>DR in the Modifiers tab to match the calculation result.</em></p>"
